{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/OS/2","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"88a0bbd6-1a9e-5ea6-8afd-1a21e29e7e0c","html":"<h3 id=\"cpu-스케줄러\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cpu-%EC%8A%A4%EC%BC%80%EC%A4%84%EB%9F%AC\" aria-label=\"cpu 스케줄러 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CPU 스케줄러</h3>\n<blockquote>\n<p>스케줄링 대상은 Ready Queue에 있는 프로세스들이다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h4 id=\"cpu-스케줄링이-결정되는-시점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cpu-%EC%8A%A4%EC%BC%80%EC%A4%84%EB%A7%81%EC%9D%B4-%EA%B2%B0%EC%A0%95%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%EC%8B%9C%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"cpu 스케줄링이 결정되는 시점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CPU 스케줄링이 결정되는 시점</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>실행(Running) 상태의 프로세스의 상태가 바뀌는 경우</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">실행</code>(Running) => <code class=\"language-text\">대기</code>(Waiting)\n=> ex. 입출력 인터럽트(I/O Interrupt)가 발생했을 때, 비선점 방식에서</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">실행</code>(Running) => <code class=\"language-text\">준비 완료</code>(Ready)\n=> ex. 타이머 인터럽트(Timer Interrupt)가 발생했을 때, 선점될 때</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">실행</code>(Running) => <code class=\"language-text\">종료</code>(Terminated)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>레디 큐(Ready Queue)에 변화가 있는 경우</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">대기</code>(Waiting) => <code class=\"language-text\">준비 완료</code>(Ready)</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"cpu-스케줄링-알고리즘\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cpu-%EC%8A%A4%EC%BC%80%EC%A4%84%EB%A7%81-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98\" aria-label=\"cpu 스케줄링 알고리즘 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CPU 스케줄링 알고리즘</h3>\n<h4 id=\"fcfsfirst-come-first-served\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fcfsfirst-come-first-served\" aria-label=\"fcfsfirst come first served permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>FCFS(First Come First Served)</h4>\n<h5 id=\"특징\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95\" aria-label=\"특징 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특징</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>비선점형 스케줄링</li>\n<li><u>먼저 온 프로세스를 먼저 서비스 해주는 방식</u></li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"문제점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"문제점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제점</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>convoy effect <a href=\"#convoy-effect\">👀</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"sjfsjortest---job---first\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sjfsjortest---job---first\" aria-label=\"sjfsjortest   job   first permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SJF(Sjortest - Job - First)</h4>\n<h5 id=\"특징-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95-1\" aria-label=\"특징 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특징</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>비선점형 스케줄링</li>\n<li>다른 프로세스가 먼저 도착했어도 <u>CPU burst time 이 짧은 프로세스에게 선 할당</u></li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"문제점-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%EC%A0%90-1\" aria-label=\"문제점 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제점</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>starvation <a href=\"#startvation\">👀</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"srtfshortest-remaining-time-first\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#srtfshortest-remaining-time-first\" aria-label=\"srtfshortest remaining time first permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>SRTF(Shortest Remaining Time First)</h4>\n<h5 id=\"특징-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95-2\" aria-label=\"특징 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특징</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>선점형 (Preemptive) 스케줄링</li>\n<li>새로운 프로세스가 도착할 때마다 새로운 스케줄링이 이루어진다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"문제점-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%EC%A0%90-2\" aria-label=\"문제점 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제점</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>starvation <a href=\"#startvation\">👀</a></li>\n<li>새로운 프로세스가 도달할 때마다 스케줄링을 다시해 CPU burst time(CPU 사용시간)을 측정할 수가 없다.<strong>?</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"priority-scheduling\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#priority-scheduling\" aria-label=\"priority scheduling permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Priority Scheduling</h4>\n<h5 id=\"특징-3\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95-3\" aria-label=\"특징 3 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특징</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><u>우선순위가 가장 높은 프로세스에게 CPU 를 할당</u>하는 스케줄링이다. 우선순위란 정수로 표현하게 되고 작은 숫자가 우선순위가 높다.</li>\n<li>선점형 스케줄링(Preemptive) 방식\n더 높은 우선순위의 프로세스가 도착하면 실행중인 프로세스를 멈추고 CPU 를 선점한다. 우선순위가 같으면 FCFS로 진행한다.</li>\n<li>비선점형 스케줄링(Non-Preemptive) 방식\n더 높은 우선순위의 프로세스가 도착하면 Ready Queue 의 Head 에 넣는다.</li>\n<li>\n<div style=\"color:#999999\">우선순위를 정하는 방법\n<ul>\n<li>내부적 우선순위 결정\n제한 시간, 기억장소 요청량, 사용 파일 수, 평균 프로세서 버스트에 대한 평균 입출력 버스트의 비율</li>\n<li>외부적 우선순위 결정\n프로세스의 중요성, 사용료를 많이 낸 사용자, 작업을 지원하는 부서, 정책적 요인</div></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"문제점-3\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%EC%A0%90-3\" aria-label=\"문제점 3 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제점</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>starvation <a href=\"#startvation\">👀</a></li>\n<li>무기한 봉쇄(Indefinite blocking) <a href=\"#%EB%AC%B4%EA%B8%B0%ED%95%9C-%EB%B4%89%EC%87%84indefinite-blocking\">👀</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"해결책\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0%EC%B1%85\" aria-label=\"해결책 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>해결책</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>aging <a href=\"#aging\">👀</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"round-robin\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#round-robin\" aria-label=\"round robin permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Round Robin</h4>\n<h5 id=\"특징-4\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%8A%B9%EC%A7%95-4\" aria-label=\"특징 4 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>특징</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>현대적인 CPU 스케줄링 (멀티태스킹을 많이 해서?)</li>\n<li>각 프로세스는 <u>동일한 크기의 할당 시간(time quantum)</u>을 갖게 된다.</li>\n<li>할당 시간이 지나면 프로세스는 <strong>선점</strong>당하고 ready queue 의 제일 뒤에 가서 다시 줄을 선다.</li>\n<li>RR은 CPU 사용시간이 랜덤한 프로세스들이 섞여있을 경우에 효율적</li>\n<li>RR이 가능한 이유는 프로세스의 context 를 save 할 수 있기 때문이다.(PCB 덕)</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"장점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9E%A5%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"장점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>장점</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Response time이 빨라진다.\nn 개의 프로세스가 ready queue 에 있고 할당시간이 q(time quantum)인 경우 각 프로세스는 q 단위로 CPU 시간의 1/n 을 얻는다. 즉, 어떤 프로세스도 (n-1)q time unit 이상 기다리지 않는다.</li>\n<li>프로세스가 기다리는 시간이 CPU 를 사용할 만큼 증가한다.\n공정한 스케줄링이라고 할 수 있다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h5 id=\"주의\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9D%98\" aria-label=\"주의 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>주의</h5>\n<p>time quantum의 길이를 신경써야 함.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>길때 : FCFS랑 다를게 없음</li>\n<li>짧을 때 : context switch도 비용이 있기 때문에 자주할수록 비용이 추가됨(overhead)</li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n<h4 id=\"개념-정리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B0%9C%EB%85%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"개념 정리 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>개념 정리</h4>\n<h5 id=\"선점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%A0%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"선점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>선점</h5>\n<p>현재 수행중인 프로세스의 남은 burst time 보다 더 짧은 CPU burst time 을 가지는 새로운 프로세스가 도착하면 CPU 를 뺏긴다.</p>\n<h5 id=\"비선점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B9%84%EC%84%A0%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"비선점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>비선점</h5>\n<p>일단 CPU 를 잡으면 CPU burst 가 완료될 때까지 CPU 를 반환하지 않는다. 할당되었던 CPU 가 반환될 때만 스케줄링이 이루어진다.</p>\n<h5 id=\"startvation\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#startvation\" aria-label=\"startvation permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>startvation</h5>\n<p>CPU burst time이 긴 프로세스는 영원히 CPU를 할당받지 못할 수 있다.</p>\n<h5 id=\"convoy-effect\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#convoy-effect\" aria-label=\"convoy effect permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>convoy effect</h5>\n<p>소요시간이 긴 프로세스가 먼저 도달하여 cpu를 혼자 점유하여 효율이 낮아지는걸 말함.</p>\n<h5 id=\"무기한-봉쇄indefinite-blocking\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B4%EA%B8%B0%ED%95%9C-%EB%B4%89%EC%87%84indefinite-blocking\" aria-label=\"무기한 봉쇄indefinite blocking permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>무기한 봉쇄(Indefinite blocking)</h5>\n<p>실행 준비는 되어있으나 CPU 를 사용못하는 프로세스를 CPU 가 무기한 대기하는 상태</p>\n<h5 id=\"aging\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#aging\" aria-label=\"aging permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>aging</h5>\n<p>아무리 우선순위가 낮은 프로세스라도 오래 기다리면 우선순위를 높여주자.</p>\n<h5 id=\"참고\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0\" aria-label=\"참고 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고</h5>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://m.blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?isHttpsRedirect=true&#x26;blogId=bycho211&#x26;logNo=220982791510\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">참고 1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%8A%A4%EC%BC%80%EC%A4%84%EB%A7%81_(%EC%BB%B4%ED%93%A8%ED%8C%85)\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">참고 2</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JaeYeopHan/Interview_Question_for_Beginner/tree/master/OS#cpu-%EC%8A%A4%EC%BC%80%EC%A4%84%EB%9F%AC\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">참고 3</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wonit.tistory.com/108\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">참고 4</a></li>\n</ul>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/OS/2","tagSlugs":["/tag/os/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2021-08-06T00:00:00","description":"CPU 스케줄러가 사용하는 스캐줄링 알고리즘을 정리해볼 생각입니다.","tags":["OS"],"title":"CPU 스케줄링 알고리즘","socialImage":{"publicURL":"/static/6522b74580d592d86ca1741a09ed47bf/state.png"}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/OS/2"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}